videos.description: Jarret Culver shows off his range as he comes up with the ball then drills a deep 3-pointer to extend Texas Tech's lead over Baylor.
videos.headline: Culver gathers loose ball, then drills deep 3-pointer

videos.headline: Moretti knocks down 3-pointer
